as
of september28, 2002, the company had $4.337billion in cash, cash equivalents, and short-term investments, virtually unchanged from the end of fiscal 2001. the primary
sources of total cash, cash equivalents, and short-term investments in fiscal 2002 were $89million in cash generated by operating activities and $105million in proceeds
