in july2001, the company acquired spruce technologies,inc. (spruce), a privately-held company that develops and markets dvd authoring products, for
$14.9million in cash. goodwill associated with the acquisition of spruce is not subject to amortization pursuant to the transition provisions of sfas no.142.
